var jQvectormaploader;
var initjvmap_map12191;
	initjvmap_map12191 = function(){
		if (typeof jQvectormaploader=="undefined"){
			 
				jQvectormaploader = jQuery.ajax({url: 'IMG/jvectormap/jquery-jvectormap-world-mill.js?1506342604', dataType: 'script', cache: true});
			
		}
		jQvectormaploader.done(function(){
			jQuery(function(){
				$('.map12191').vectorMap({
					map: 'world_mill',
					backgroundColor: 'transparent',
					height:'100%',
					width:'100%',
					regionsSelectable: true,
					zoomOnScroll: true,
					regionStyle: {
						initial: {
							'fill': '#b9b9b9',
							'fill-opacity': 1,
							'stroke': 'none',
							'stroke-width': 0,
							'stroke-opacity': 1
						},
						hover: {
							"fill-opacity": 0.8
						},
						selected: {
							fill: '#336699'
						},
						selectedHover: {}
					},
					focusOn: {
						x: 0,
						y: 0,
						scale: 0
					},
					onResize: function(e){
						var mapObj = $('.map12191').vectorMap('get', 'mapObject');
						mapObj.updateSize();
					},
					onRegionClick: function(element, code, region){
						// Récupère la fiche pays suivant l'ID de la rubrique
						var mapObj = $('.map12191').vectorMap('get', 'mapObject');
						
						var id_cav = mapObj['regions'][code]['config']['id_cav_fr'];
						if(typeof(id_cav) != 'undefined' && id_cav != false) {
							window.location = id_cav
						} else {
							return false;
						}
					},
					onRegionTipShow: function(e, el, code){
						if ($.inArray(code,[ "_2", "_0", "PR","FR","FK","NC","AQ"]) != '-1'){
							e.preventDefault();
						}
						
						var data = $('.map12191').vectorMap('get', 'mapObject').mapData;
						if(typeof(data.paths[code].name_fr) != "undefined"){
							el.html(data.paths[code].name_fr);
						}
						else{
							e.preventDefault();
						}
					},
					onRegionOver:function(e, code, region){
						
						var data = $('.map12191').vectorMap('get', 'mapObject').mapData;
						if(typeof(data.paths[code].name_fr) == "undefined"){
							e.preventDefault();
						}
					},
					onRegionOut: function(event, code, region){},
					onLabelShow: function(event, label, code){},
					onViewportChange: function(e, scale, transX, transY){
						var mapObj = $('.map12191').vectorMap('get', 'mapObject');
						mapObj.resize();
					},
					onMarkerClick: function(element, code, region){
						// Récupère la fiche pays suivant l'ID de la rubrique
						var mapObj = $('.map12191').vectorMap('get', 'mapObject');
						
						var url_cav = mapObj['markers'][code]['config']['id_cav_fr'];
						if(url_cav != false && typeof(url_cav) != 'undefined') {
							window.location = url_cav
						} else {
							return false;
						}
					},
					onMarkerTipShow: function(e, el, code){
						var data = $('.map12191').vectorMap('get', 'mapObject');
						if(typeof(data.markers[code].config.name_fr) != "undefined"){
							el.html(data.markers[code].config.name_fr);
						}
						else{
							e.preventDefault();
						}
					},
					markerStyle: {
						initial: {
							fill: '#ededed',
							stroke: '#383f47',
							"stroke-width": 1,
							r: 3
						},
						hover: {
							"fill-opacity": 0.8,
							"stroke-width": 1
						},
						selected: {
							fill: '#336699',
							r: 5
						}
					},
					markers: markers
			});
			
		});
	});
}	

	
$(document).ready(function($) {
	$('.map12191').parents('div').find('.menu_zonegeo, .liens_continents').on('click', 'button', function(){
		if($(this).is('.monde')){
			$('.map12191').vectorMap('set', 'focus', {scale: 1, x: 0, y: 0, animate: true});
		} else if($(this).is('.anmo')) {
			$('.map12191').vectorMap('set', 'focus', {regions: ['MR','IR','_3'], animate: true});
		} else if($(this).is('.afrique')) {
			$('.map12191').vectorMap('set', 'focus', {regions: ['MA', 'MR', 'ZA'], animate: true});
		} else if($(this).is('.ameriques') || $(this).is('.amerique')) {
			$('.map12191').vectorMap('set', 'focus', {regions: ['CA', 'CL'], animate: true});
		} else if($(this).is('.asie')) {
			$('.map12191').vectorMap('set', 'focus', {regions: ['IR', 'JP'], animate: true});
		} else if($(this).is('.europe')) {
			$('.map12191').vectorMap('set', 'focus', {regions: ['IS', 'UA', 'GR'], animate: true});
		} else if($(this).is('.oceanie')) {
			$('.map12191').vectorMap('set', 'focus', {regions: ['ID', 'FJ', 'NZ'], animate: true});
		} 
	});

	if(navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf('firefox') > -1 && $('.map12191').is(':visible')){
		if (typeof jQuery.ajax == "undefined") {
			jQuery(initjvmap_map12191);
		} else {
			initjvmap_map12191();
		}
	} else if (navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf('firefox') == -1) {
		if (typeof jQuery.ajax == "undefined"){
			jQuery(initjvmap_map12191);
		} else {
			initjvmap_map12191();
		}
	}
});
